    • Method Detail

      • enroll

        void enroll(String accessToken,
          Map<String,String> enrollParams,
          URI baseUaaUri,
          URL enrollUrl)
            throws PredixCloudIdentityException
        Enroll this device in a specified UAA instance in Predix cloud.
        Parameters:
        accessToken - bearer token which grants access to Predix Cloud Enrollment Service
        enrollParams - map of key value enrollment parameters. Will get passed along with request to enrollment service
        baseUaaUri - The base UAA URI (not including anything after the host) to use to enroll this device
        enrollUrl - The URL for device enrollment to use. Should end with /v1/enroll
        Throws:
        PredixCloudIdentityException - If enrollment fails

      • enrollCertificateBased

        void enrollCertificateBased()
                            throws PredixCloudIdentityException
        Enroll this device using certificate based enrollment to Predix Machine Edge Manager. Calls enrollCertificateBased(String, String, char[], URL) using the available values from Predix Cloud Identity Service
        Throws:
        PredixCloudIdentityException - if enrollment fails
        Since:
        16.2

      • enrollCertificateBased

        void enrollCertificateBased(String macAddr,
                          String deviceId,
                          char[] sharedSecret,
                          URL enrollURL)
                            throws PredixCloudIdentityException
        Enroll this device using certificate based enrollment to Predix Machine Edge Manager.
        Parameters:
        macAddr - MAC address of device
        deviceId - device ID of device
        sharedSecret - shared secret to access endpoint
        enrollURL - Edge Manager enrollment URL
        Throws:
        PredixCloudIdentityException - if enrollment fails
        Since:
        16.2
